trans-unit.source: Exposes <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement3D"></xref> types to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

By default, any class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> uses UIElement3DAutomationPeer to communicate with [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 기본적으로 모든 클래스에서 상속 되 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>UIElement3DAutomationPeer를 사용 하 여 통신할 수 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>

trans-unit.source: If you create a class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, you may want to provide an automation peer to support the functionality of your class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>프로그램 클래스의 기능을 지원 하도록 자동화 피어를 제공 하는 것이 경우가</xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> 에서 상속 되는 클래스를 만드는 경우

trans-unit.source: Override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return a string that represents the type of the element associated with the UIElement3DAutomationPeer.
trans-unit.target: 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>메서드는 UIElement3DAutomationPeer와 연결 된 요소의 형식을 나타내는 문자열을 반환 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you create a class called `My3DElement` and an automation peer called `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return the string "My3DElement".
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어, 라는 클래스를 만들면 `My3DElement` 라는 자동화 피어와 `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>"My3DElement" 문자열을 반환 하는 메서드.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: If your class matches one of the known control types, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> method to return that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.
trans-unit.target: 클래스에는 알려진된 컨트롤 형식 중 하 나와 일치, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> 반환 하는 메서드</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> 를 재정의합니다

trans-unit.source: Note that although the existing <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> values are generally associated with 2D controls, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> indicates a control's functionality, not its appearance.
trans-unit.target: 하지만 기존 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>값은 일반적으로 2D 컨트롤과 연결 된 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>모양이 아닌 컨트롤의 기능을 나타냅니다.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>
